Package: snapKrig
Title: Fast Kriging with Kronecker Covariance
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Dean", "Koch", , "dkoch@ualberta.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8849-859X"))
Description: Functions for fitting geostatistical models and kriging with
    gridded data with spatially separable covariance functions (Kronecker
    covariance). Kronecker products are used to simplify computations for
    likelihood, conditional mean, and more.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
